title: Bibaho Obhijaan
subTitle: While Rajat's wife is extremely religious, Anupam's wife is a busy activist. Soon, Rajat and Anupam face hilarious situations in their marriage as they are frustrated with their wives.

title: Bhooter Bhabishyat
subTitle: A haunted house is getting converted into a shopping centre. However, a group of spirits residing in the house use various tactics to save their resting place.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Parvati forsakes her love for Lord Shiva to honour her parents' desire. Later, Mainavati sets terms for approving the marriage arrangement.

title: Besh Korechi Prem Korechi
subTitle: A man helps the sister of a gangster elope on the day of her wedding. However, he finds himself in a bigger mess when he falls in love with the gangster's other sister.

title: Lal Kothi
subTitle: Tanu accidentally hits a man with her car on a stormy night but decides not to inform the police. However, a mysterious stranger surfaces who claims to be a witness and blackmails her.

title: Sansar Sangram
subTitle: The death of his father leaves Anand's life in sudden sorrow and upheaval. Soon, he navigates the challenges of supporting his family on his own two shoulders.

title: Poran Jaye Jolia Re
subTitle: A young man, Rabin, meets three different women at different stages in his life. The relationship he shares with these women, though very different from each other, help him grow as a person.

title: Amader Sansar
subTitle: Soumen goes against his mother's will and decides to tie the knot with his teacher's daughter in order to make him happy.

title: Premi
subTitle: Sumit, a football player, loses his leg while trying to save Rahul, his best friend. Fate plays a cruel joke when the girl Rahul loves is about to be married off to Sumit.

title: Shiva
subTitle: When a police inspector manages to capture a member of a human trafficking ring, the gang leader vows to take revenge. He relentlessly hunts for the officer with an intention to kill him.

title: Shiva
subTitle: When a police inspector manages to capture a member of a human trafficking ring, the gang leader vows to take revenge. He relentlessly hunts for the officer with an intention to kill him.

title: Antarleen
subTitle: Aniket Sanyal, a detective, is forced to resume work during his much-needed, long vacation after a mysterious death of a tourist.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Lord Vishnu asks Kaamdev for help, wanting him to disturb Lord Shiva's meditative state, and Tarakasura reaches Kailash to attack.

title: Akritagya
subTitle: Trishna's maternal uncle kills her father in order to seek the latter's property. Later, Trishna strives to take revenge, however, dark secrets are revealed.

title: Debdas
subTitle: Debdas resorts to drinking after he is unable to marry the love of his life, Paro. However, as his situation worsens, he decides to pay her a visit before he dies.

title: Dui Prithibi
subTitle: A rich man falls in love with an idealistic medical student. However, when circumstances force them apart, he learns the true meaning and value of love.

title: Satrur Muqubila
subTitle: Awbhoy, a dedicated police officer, develops a deep romantic interest in a young woman attending a job interview while undergoing training.

title: Mahaan
subTitle: Ajit adopts Chandu, who later falls for a girl named Mala. Trouble arises for Chandu when Mala's father turns out to be Ajit's boss.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: After his wife's demise, a man tries to start over with her estranged family. When he falls in love with his wife's twin, he fears that his efforts to mend broken relations will go to waste.

title: Kencho Khunrte Keute
subTitle: Gyanoda loses his son and daughter-in-law, leaving his granddaughter Parama as a spoilt child. To discipline her, he leaves a will which requires her to marry to gain full inheritance access.

title: Swapner Din
subTitle: Paresh goes on a mission to educate and enlighten the people of rural West Bengal. With many hurdles on his way, he struggles with turning his dream into reality.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Lord Vishnu stops Tarakasura with his attack. Lord Shiva awakes furiously and punishes Kaamdev by turning him into ashes.

title: Jamai No 1
subTitle: A businessman weds his two eldest daughters to men who now depend on him. However, things take a turn when his third daughter marries a thief.

title: Debota
subTitle: After getting subjected to injustice since childhood, Rana decides to rob the rich and distribute the wealth amongst the poor. However, things get difficult when he gets accused of killing his lover.

title: Chirodini Tumi Je Amar
subTitle: Pallavi, a rich, spoilt girl, falls in love with Krishna, a scooter mechanic, and gets married without her parents' approval. The situation takes an ugly turn when her family tries to separate them.

title: Chhoto Bou
subTitle: A mother-in-law treats her daughters-in-law, Mamta, Tandra and Deepa, according to their husband's income. However, when she falls ill, she realises her folly.

title: Total Dadagiri
subTitle: College students Joy and Jonaki fall in love with each other, much to the distress of her father, who is totally opposed to their relationship.

title: Premer Kahini
subTitle: Akash falls in love with Barsha but loses contact with her due to unforeseeable circumstances. While attending a marriage ceremony, he is shocked to realise that the bride is none other than Barsha.

title: Indrajit
subTitle: Indrajit is an honest police officer who punishes Raja, an MLA's son, for raping a girl. The MLA then kidnaps the former's son and demands Raja's release.
